trans-unit.source: InteropBitmap enables developers to improve rendering performance of non-[!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ui#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uisharpplural-md.md)] that are hosted by [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] in interoperability scenarios.
trans-unit.target: InteropBitmap kunnen ontwikkelaars verbeteren de prestaties van de rendering van niet -[!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ui#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uisharpplural-md.md)] die worden gehost door [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] in interoperabiliteit scenario's.

trans-unit.source: Forces the hosted non-[!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ui](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] to be rendered.
trans-unit.target: Zorgt ervoor dat het gehoste niet -[!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ui](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] moet worden gerenderd.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Windows.Interop.InteropBitmap"></xref> instance is frozen and cannot have its members written to.
trans-unit.target: De <xref href="System.Windows.Interop.InteropBitmap"> </xref> exemplaar is vastgezet en kunnen niet hebben de leden naar geschreven.

trans-unit.source: Forces the specified area of the hosted non-[!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ui](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] to be rendered.
trans-unit.target: Zorgt ervoor dat het opgegeven gebied van de gehoste niet -[!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ui](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] moet worden gerenderd.

trans-unit.source: The area of the hosted non-[!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ui](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] to be rendered.
trans-unit.target: Het gebied van de gehoste niet -[!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ui](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] moet worden gerenderd.

trans-unit.source: If this parameter is null, the entire non-[!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ui](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] is rendered.
trans-unit.target: Als deze parameter is null, het gehele niet -[!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ui](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] wordt weergegeven.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Windows.Interop.InteropBitmap"></xref> instance is frozen and cannot have its members written to.
trans-unit.target: De <xref href="System.Windows.Interop.InteropBitmap"> </xref> exemplaar is vastgezet en kunnen niet hebben de leden naar geschreven.
